text: Thank you @POTUS for offering a comprehensive plan to fix our nation’s #infrastructure. Looking forward to working with @POTUS and @SecElaineChao on this important issue!
Congrats @david_redl for clearing @SenateCommerce! Great working w/ you on spectrum & more @HouseCommerce. You deserve @SenateFloor vote!
I want to thank U.S. Capitol Police for apprehending the shooter this morning. I have always known them to be heroic & they proved it today.
I am deeply horrified by what happened this morning. Steve is a good friend of mine. Praying for him and everyone affected.
Just hit 24 hrs @HouseCommerce health care markup. I will work as long as it takes to get Kentuckians the health care they deserve.
#Obamacare meant chaos for our insurance markets. American Health Care Act will stabilize the market, meaning affordable care.
The American Health Care Act allows individuals to control their health care instead of bureaucrats in DC. #BetterWay #RepealAndReplace
For Obamacare, we saw bill less than 24 hrs before markup. The American Health Care Act is a #BetterWay.
.@RepGregWalden has assembled a great team of leaders and staff at @HouseCommerce to tackle Obamacare. I’m ready to get to work.
Congrats to @michaelburgess, our new Health Subcommittee Chair. I'm ready to work w/ you as Vice Chair to fix our broken health care system.
“Your premiums will go down.” TRUTH: Premiums and deductibles are on the rise under #Obamacare.
"If you like your health plan, you can keep it.” No, President Obama – millions are losing their plans. We must fix the failed #Obamacare.
President Obama is trying to defend #Obamacare at the Capitol today. We need real solutions – not a failed bill that has hurt Americans.
My bill, HR 921, just passed unanimously at @HouseCommerce full committee markup!
Remembering today the teachers who encouraged and believed in me as a student. Thank a #KY02 teacher today! #TeacherAppreciationDay
Visit my Facebook page to vote for the “Facebook Favorite” among each county’s winning art! The winning piece will hang in my D.C. office!
Wishing @SpeakerRyan the happiest of birthdays!
Thanks to my colleagues in the House for supporting the Early Hearing Detection & Intervention Act of 2015!
Calling in to the @joeelliottshow - Tune in now!
Unprecedented bipartisan committee effort #CuresIn4Words @ECcures
Innovation today, Cures tomorrow #Curesin4Words
The president scored #Obamacare 8/10. With higher premiums & lost coverage, we're only gaining more headaches. What grade would you give it?
My thoughts & prayers are with the family of Sen. Wendell Ford. The Owensboro native had a long history of service to the Commonwealth.
US @StateDept confirmed that #KeystoneXL will support approx 42,000 jobs #TimeToBuild  #SOTU
Looking forward to passing much needed education reforms with my colleagues on @EdWorkforce Committee this year. #SOTU
